        "txt": { "type": "text", "settings": { "text": "<p>We started Proferlo with one question: why does good furniture have to cost so much?</p><p>The Australian furniture market gives you two extremes — legacy brands with luxury price tags, or flat-pack fast furniture that looks okay for a season and falls apart by the next. Neither felt right.</p><p>So we built a third option.</p><p>Proferlo is a fully vertically integrated furniture brand, based in Brisbane, Queensland. We own our manufacturing, control our supply chain, and manage our own delivery — no importers, no wholesalers, no retail floor markups. What you pay goes toward the furniture, not the layers in between.</p>", "text_size": "text-base" } }
