        "txt": { "type": "text", "settings": { "text": "<p>All Proferlo timber furniture is FSC certified, meaning the wood is sourced from responsibly managed forests that meet strict environmental and social standards.</p><p>Our products also meet CARB2 certification - a rigorous standard for low formaldehyde emissions that ensures the furniture is safe for your home and family.</p><p>These aren't marketing badges. They're independent, third-party verified standards that we hold ourselves to.</p>", "text_size": "text-base" } }
